data.description:
TURN-KEY 4 BEDROOM!! This home has been fully renovated with a true open floor plan people love. There are 3 Full bathrooms and a huge re-designed kitchen that will not disappoint! This property is also neighbors with a local church and has a ton of history in the neighborhood. 
Check out the bonus room inside the detached garage, perfect for games or an extra bedroom! BRAND NEW 5 TON HVAC system to keep you cool this summer with manufacturer lifetime warranty! Lots of new construction happening in this neighborhood, and it's also on a corner lot. Perfect place for someone to call home!
